# KV baseline raw runs can contain multi-GB Mooncake/LMCache cache data.
/artifacts/kv_baseline/*
!/artifacts/kv_baseline/README.md
!/artifacts/kv_baseline/manifests/
!/artifacts/kv_baseline/manifests/**

# Cross-model runtime raw runs can also contain large Mooncake KV payloads.
/artifacts/cross_model_runtime/*
!/artifacts/cross_model_runtime/README.md
!/artifacts/cross_model_runtime/manifests/
!/artifacts/cross_model_runtime/manifests/**
